channel.title: Sycrat's AIO V1.05 (Idea taken from money67)
channel.description:
Hey guys!
I'm learning delphi in school at the moment and I saw money67's batch space saver thingo and I thought I might have a go at it. Keep in mind this is my first proper program (unless you count helloworld as a proper program =\) so judge, but give constructive criticism :). If you want me to edit this program for your needs or add programs to it or change certain programs paths just post here with what you want done :). If you know a bit of delphi and want to edit it yourself I've put the delphi files in there aswell.
Hope you like it :), have fun with it.
[url=http://sycrat.info/downloads/Sycrat's Space Saver.zip]Just the exe[/url] [url=http://sycrat.info/downloads/S3 Delphi Files.zip]Delphi Source Files[/url]
Currently in V1.05 Changes since V1.04:
[ul][li]Autosaving memo added[/li][/ul]
If you edit it do not redistribute or remove my name please.
